{"tid":2134484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭月娥：正式宣布引用《緊急法》心，押後立法會選舉一年","createTime":"2020-07-31T17:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T17:51:41.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3de5e84a9fd7d2ca900c1397b8e9f4767160c49b","tid":2134484,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:48:08.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥宣布，因應疫情立法會換屆選舉押後一年，日期延至為2021年9月5日舉行。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，緊急規例條例只能將立法會選舉日期推遲一年，而未能處理立法會未來一年將出現「真空期」問題。她引述國務院指，如何處理立法機關空缺，中央將依法提請人大常委會作出決定。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，已就事件向中央政府呈交緊急報告、尋求支持和指示，國務院已回覆，表示支持行政長官會同行政會議，基於公眾利益和香港實際情況，依法作出立法會選舉推遲一年的決定。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，將撤銷有關9月6日換屆選舉的公告，選舉程序即告終結。政府將向有選舉開支的候選人，按申索指引支付款項及退回按金予候選人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541085-20200731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541085-20200731.htm&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOdHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=bec2a8b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541085-20200731.htm&h=9f57fcee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541085-20200731.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8f868b97505f5cd936d39ea0551418d8a8995695","tid":2134484,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T17:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}